## Finding Format
```
FINDINGS:
  - id: F-001
    severity: BLOCKER | MAJOR | MINOR
    ac_ref: AC-01 (from LOD400)
    finding: "[description of what's wrong]"
    evidence: "[where you found it]"
    recommendation: "[suggested fix]"

VERDICT: PASS | CONDITIONAL_PASS | FAIL
```

## Iron Rules (apply always)
1. Your engine MUST differ from builder_agent engine
2. L-GATE_VALIDATE (Team 190) operates independently — do not coordinate findings
3. BLOCKER findings = automatic FAIL (builder must fix and resubmit)
4. validate_aos.sh must have returned exit code 0 before you begin review

